      • create

        public MkvMQ create​(String name,
                    MkvType type,
                    MkvMQConf conf)
             throws MkvException
        Constructs and publishes a newly allocated MkvMQ object with the given name and type. Some behavioral aspect of the Message Queue can be customized through the conf object.
        Parameters:
        name - the queue name.
        type - the queue type.
        conf - the queue configuration object.
        Returns:
        the newly created MkvMQ object.
        Throws:
        MkvException - in case the message queue or its associated type cannot be published

      • create

        public MkvMQ create​(String name,
                    MkvType type,
                    MkvMQConf conf,
                    MkvMQListener lner)
             throws MkvException
        Constructs and publishes a newly allocated MkvMQ object with the given name and type. Some behavioral aspect of the Message Queue can be customized through the conf object.
        Parameters:
        name - the queue name.
        type - the queue type.
        conf - the queue configuration object.
        lner - a listener invoked on message queue destruction.
        Returns:
        the newly created MkvMQ object.
        Throws:
        MkvException - in case the message queue or its associated type cannot be published

      • createSubscription

        public MkvMQSubscribe createSubscription​(String messagequeue,
                                         MkvMQSubscribeListener lner,
                                         MkvMQSubscribeConf conf)
        Subscribes to the specified queue using the provided listener and configuration class.
        Parameters:
        messagequeue - The Message Queue to be subscribed
        lner - The MkvMQListener to be associated with the subscription
        conf - A MkvMQSubscribeConf configuration object
        Returns:
        a new MkvMQSubscribe object, or null if the queue is already subscribed.

                                         MkvMQSubscribeListener lner,
                                         MkvMQSubscribeConf conf,
                                         MkvMQAckRequestListener ackReqLner)
        Subscribes to the specified queue using the provided: listener, configuration class, and listener for acknowledge requests coming from the publisher.
        Parameters:
        messagequeue - The Message Queue to be subscribed
        lner - The MkvMQListener to be associated with the subscription
        conf - A MkvMQSubscribeConf configuration object
        ackReqLner - A MkvMQAckRequestListener to be associated with the subscription
        Returns:
